-  Make sure to provide fuel to entities that require it, such as burner mining drills and boilers.

### Errors when entities have no ingredients

### Errors when entities are not connected
-  Verify that entities like steam engines are properly connected to the rest of the system.

### Errors when entities are not plugged into the electric network
-  Confirm that entities like electricity groups are plugged into the electric network.

### Errors when belt groups are empty
-  Check that belt groups have items to transport.

### Errors when pipe groups are empty or have full output
-  Monitor pipe groups to ensure they are functioning correctly and not causing issues with the system.
